{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"どの演目もすごかったけど、ハロハピのオープニングアクトも\nすっごく良かったよ！\n演奏も演出も良かったし、衣装もサーカスらしくて可愛かったね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"本当ですか？\n実はあのライブ衣装、私と美咲ちゃんで作ったんです","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"うん、美咲ちゃんからも、\n『花音さんが一生懸命頑張ってた』って教えてもらったよ。\nお疲れ様、花音ちゃん","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"ありがとうございます……！\nはい。みんなのお陰で、すごく頑張れました","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"みんなも、イベントの準備に、宣伝に……\nステージ以外のところでも大活躍でした","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"……って、私は衣装の直しをしてたので、\nみんなが宣伝してる様子を見られなかったんですけどね。えへへ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"でも、そうやって別々のところで準備を進めて、\nみんな、私が衣装を間に合わせるって信じてくれてて……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"そう思ったら私、いつも以上の力が出たんです。\nみんなが信じてくれた私なんだから、胸を張らなきゃって","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev164-me2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCh